code: @Override public boolean supportsParameter(MethodParameter param) {     return checkAnnotatedParamNoReactiveWrapper(param, Value.class, (ann, type) -> true). }

@Override protected NamedValueInfo createNamedValueInfo(MethodParameter parameter) {     Value ann = parameter.getParameterAnnotation(Value.class).     Assert.state(ann != null, "No Value annotation").     return new ExpressionValueNamedValueInfo(ann). }
@Override protected Object resolveNamedValue(String name, MethodParameter parameter, ServerWebExchange exchange) {     // No name to resolve     return null. }
@Override protected void handleMissingValue(String name, MethodParameter parameter) {     throw new UnsupportedOperationException("@Value is never required: " + parameter.getMethod()). }
